.JPG"> </a> </div> </figure> </div> <div class="card card-article-mobile-only width-full flex-container-column flex-2"> <h4 class="promo-header spaced spaced-xs spaced-bottom spaced-top font-normal"><a class="unstyled-link " href="/2020/06/03/tips-paying-down-credit-card-debt/"> Tips on paying down credit card debt </a></h4> <div class="spaced color-grey-dark font-md hidden-sm" data-pb-field="custom.blurbText_" data-pb-url-field="custom.blurbUrl_" data-pb-field-type="text" data-pb-placeholder="#">It’s normal to turn to credit cards in an emergency, which can be stressful, but personal finance expert Kim Palmer with NerdWallet says you can’t let it get to you.</div> <div class="byline-timestamp-container flex-container-column flex-desktop-row spaced spaced-top spaced-xs align-items-start"> <div class="byline-wrapper flex-container-row hidden-sm"> <span class="byline">By&nbsp;</span> <h3 class="byline bold"> <span><span>Rachel DePompa</span></span> </h3> <span class="spaced spaced-right spaced-md"></span> </div> <div class="font-sm color-grey byline-wrapper flex-container-row hidden-sm"> Published June 3, 2020 at 6:43 PM </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col desktop-12 tablet-12 mobile-12"> <div class="card skin"> <div class="card-media width-full"> <div class="align-items-center flex-container-row justify-space-between"> <div class="width-full spaced card-media flex-reverse spaced-left spaced-lg flex"> <figure class=""> <div class="width-full img-container aspect-ratio-2x1"> <a href="/2020/06/03/henrico-group-marches-willow-lawn-lee-monument/"> <img class="width-full " alt="Henrico group marches from Willow Lawn to Lee monument" src="https://www.nbc12.com/resizer/055lNP-G20BCaqT-w0IP6G7W54s=/1200x600/cloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com/raycom/PYNHNRKNCJCWZINZ4IVRI4YJXE.jpg"> </a> </div> </figure> </div> <div class="card card-article-mobile-only width-full flex-container-column flex-2"> <h4 class="promo-header spaced spaced-xs spac